Chef Wanted with Anne Burrell - Season 3, Episode 7





Small Plates, Big Stakes

Southern California tapas destination, Cafe Sevilla, is in need for a new Executive Chef to oversee their three locations. Anne Burrell brings in four candidates who are tested on their ability to create a tapas platter and show a contemporary take on a classic Spanish dish.




Original Air Date: 12-Sep-2013
